name: DashDash
0:
”Alexa open dash dash”
”Try the letter E”
”Is it the word sea?”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: dash dash
des:
This is a word guessing game similar to hangman, but without the references to violence.

-Discover the secret word by guessing its letters.
-Shout out the word to make your final guess
-Ask Alexa for hints
-Set up a game with your chosen word to challenge a friend or your orthography skills

Have fun!
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
